chapter:
Installation on Windows systems


 The official releases of PHP on Windows are recommended for production use,
 but PHP can also be built from source.



 PHP can also be installed on Azure App Services
 (aka Microsoft Azure, Windows Azure, or (Windows) Azure Web Apps).



 The Installation section of the
 frequently asked questions covers common installation and
 configuration issues that may be encountered.


